        "query": "source: instance_bill and ProductCode:oss | select Region, \"存储类型\", \"计费项\", case when \"用量\" is null then '0' else \"用量\" end as \"用量\", case when \"费用\" is null then 0.0 else \"费用\" end as \"费用\", case when \"同比上月\" is null then '0.0%' else \"同比上月\" end as \"同比上月\" from ( select case when rnk1 =1 then Region else '' end as Region , case when rnk2 = 1 then class else '' end  as \"存储类型\",BillingItem as \"计费项\", concat(cast( round(Usage,3) as varchar),' (' , UsageUnit,')') as\"用量\", \"费用\",concat(cast(round(feepercent,3) as varchar) ,'%') as \"同比上月\" from(  select *, sum(\"费用\") over(partition by Region) as regionFee,sum(\"费用\") over(partition by Region,class) as RegionClassFee , rank() over(partition by Region order by \"费用\" desc) as rnk1,rank() over(partition by Region, class order by \"费用\" desc) as rnk2  from ( select region,class, billingitem, usagediff[1] as Usage, usagediff[3]*100-100 as UsagePercent, usageunit, feediff[1] as \"费用\", case when is_nan( feediff[3]*100-100) then 0.0 else feediff[3]*100-100 end as feePercent from( select region,class, billingitem, compare(usage,2592000) as usagediff, arbitrary(usageUnit) as usageunit, compare(\"费用\",2592000) as feediff from( select Region ,split_part(InstanceId,';',2) as class, BillingItem, sum(Usage) as usage, arbitrary(UsageUnit) as UsageUnit, round(sum(PretaxAmount),3) as \"费用\"  from log group by Region,class,BillingItem  ) group by region,class,billingitem) ) )order by regionFee desc, RegionClassFee desc ,\"费用\" desc )  limit 1000",
